 120:.././crypto/tiny-AES128-C/aes.c **** // x to th e power (i-1) being powers of x (x is denoted as {02}) in the field GF(2^8)
 121:.././crypto/tiny-AES128-C/aes.c **** // Note that i starts at 1, not 0).
